{"comments":"Grade - variable font weight adjustment without changing metrics.\n\nUnlike FontWeight, Grade adjusts the apparent weight (stroke thickness)\nwithout affecting the font's advance widths or bounding boxes. This allows\nweight adjustments that don't cause text reflow.\n\n## Use Cases\n- Dark mode: Reduce grade to compensate for halation (text appearing bolder)\n- Hover states: Increase grade without layout shift\n- Print vs screen: Adjust for ink spread vs light emission\n- Accessibility: Boost contrast without changing metrics\n\n## CSS Mapping\nMaps to the 'GRAD' variation axis in OpenType variable fonts.\n\n## Range\nTypically -200 to +200, where 0 is the default design.\nNegative values are lighter, positive values are bolder.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[66,26],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/Grade.purs","start":[66,15]},"title":"Grade"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","Grade"],"Grade"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[68,36],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/Grade.purs","start":[68,1]},"title":"eqGrade"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","Grade"],"Grade"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[69,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/Grade.purs","start":[69,1]},"title":"ordGrade"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[]